extendedInfo.description: This New General Knowledge Questions app, powered by a huge data-set of questions, is there to help you out whenever you are preparing for any general knowledge quiz/exam.It contains the questions from various popular past quizzes, and has the best set of trivia questions.Our General Knowledge experts make sure you get updated questions every day, without updating the app.With the wide variety of regularly updating questions, and a very easy to use interface, this app is likely to be your best source of knowledge for anything related to INDIA.
